#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.43"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.43:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.43:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga "
msgstr "4. Deities "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.43:0.3"
msgid "43. Dutiyaniddasasutta "
msgstr "43. Graduation (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.43:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "an7.43:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.43:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya kosambiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisi. "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, entered Kosambi for alms. "

msgctxt "an7.43:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmato ānandassa etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then it occurred to him, "

msgctxt "an7.43:1.5"
msgid "“atippago kho tāva kosambiyaṃ piṇḍāya carituṃ. "
msgstr "“It’s too early to wander for alms in Kosambi. "

msgctxt "an7.43:1.6"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkameyyan”ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t I go to the monastery of the wanderers who follow other paths?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.43:1.7"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā tehi aññatitthiyehi paribbājakehi saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then he went to the monastery of the wanderers who follow other paths, and exchanged greetings with the wanderers there. "

msgctxt "an7.43:1.8"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.43:2.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ ayamantarākathā udapādi: "
msgstr "Now at that time while those wanderers who follow other paths were sitting together this discussion came up among them, "

msgctxt "an7.43:2.2"
msgid "“yo hi koci, āvuso, dvādasavassāni paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carati, ‘niddaso bhikkhū’ti alaṃvacanāyā”ti. "
msgstr "“Reverends, anyone who lives the full and pure spiritual life for twelve years is qualified to be called a ‘graduate mendicant’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.38, sc3
msgctxt "an7.43:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ bhāsitaṃ neva abhinandi nappaṭikkosi. "
msgstr "Ānanda neither approved nor dismissed that statement of the wanderers who follow other paths. "

msgctxt "an7.43:3.2"
msgid "Anabhinanditvā appaṭikkositvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi: "
msgstr "He got up from his seat, thinking, "

msgctxt "an7.43:3.3"
msgid "“bhagavato santike etassa bhāsitassa atthaṃ ājānissāmī”ti. "
msgstr "“I will learn the meaning of this statement from the Buddha himself.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.43:3.4"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando kosambiyaṃ piṇḍāya caritvā pacchābhattaṃ piṇḍapātapaṭikkanto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Ānanda wandered for alms in Kosambi. After the meal, on his return from alms-round, he went to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and told him what had happened, adding: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an7.43:4.1"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, bhante, pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya kosambiṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:4.2"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, etadahosi: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:4.3"
msgid "‘atippago kho tāva kosambiyaṃ piṇḍāya carituṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:4.4"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkameyyan’ti … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:4.5"
msgid "tehi saddhiṃ sammodiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:4.6"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an7.43:5.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana, bhante, samayena tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ sannisinnānaṃ sannipatitānaṃ ayamantarākathā udapādi: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:5.2"
msgid "‘yo hi koci, āvuso, dvādasavassāni paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carati, niddaso bhikkhūti alaṃvacanāyā’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:5.3"
msgid "Atha khvāhaṃ, bhante, tesaṃ aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ bhāsitaṃ neva abhinandiṃ nappaṭikkosiṃ. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:5.4"
msgid "Anabhinanditvā, appaṭikkositvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamiṃ: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:5.5"
msgid "‘bhagavato santike etassa bhāsitassa atthaṃ ājānissāmī’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.43:5.6"
msgid "Sakkā nu kho, bhante, imasmiṃ dhammavinaye kevalaṃ vassagaṇanamattena niddaso bhikkhu paññāpetun”ti? "
msgstr "“Sir, in this teaching and training can we describe a mendicant as a ‘graduate’ solely because they have completed a certain number of years?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an7.43:6.1"
msgid "“Na kho, ānanda, sakkā imasmiṃ dhammavinaye kevalaṃ vassagaṇanamattena niddaso bhikkhu paññāpetuṃ. "
msgstr "“No, Ānanda, we cannot. "

msgctxt "an7.43:6.2"
msgid "Satta kho imāni, ānanda, niddasavatthūni mayā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā paveditāni. "
msgstr "These are the seven qualifications for graduation that I make known after realizing them with my own insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.39, sc7
msgctxt "an7.43:7.1"
msgid "Katamāni satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.43:7.2"
msgid "Idhānanda, bhikkhu, saddho hoti, hirīmā hoti, ottappī hoti, bahussuto hoti, āraddhavīriyo hoti, satimā hoti, paññavā hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when someone is faithful, conscientious, prudent, learned, energetic, mindful, and wise. "

msgctxt "an7.43:7.3"
msgid "Imāni kho, ānanda, satta niddasavatthūni mayā sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā paveditāni. "
msgstr "These are the seven qualifications for graduation that I make known after realizing them with my own insight. "

msgctxt "an7.43:7.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, ānanda, sattahi niddasavatthūhi samannāgato bhikkhu dvādasa cepi vassāni paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carati, ‘niddaso bhikkhū’ti alaṃvacanāya; "
msgstr "A mendicant who has these seven qualifications for graduation is qualified to be called a ‘graduate mendicant’. This is so whether they have lived the full and pure spiritual life for twelve years, "

msgctxt "an7.43:7.5"
msgid "catubbīsati cepi vassāni paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carati, ‘niddaso bhikkhū’ti alaṃvacanāya; "
msgstr "twenty-four years, "

msgctxt "an7.43:7.6"
msgid "chattiṃsati cepi vassāni paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carati, ‘niddaso bhikkhū’ti alaṃvacanāya, aṭṭhacattārīsañcepi vassāni paripuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ carati, ‘niddaso bhikkhū’ti alaṃvacanāyā”ti. "
msgstr "thirty-six years, or forty-eight years.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.43:7.7"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.43:7.8"
msgid "Devatāvaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an7.43:8.1"
msgid "Appamādo hirī ceva, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.43:8.2"
msgid "dve suvacā duve mittā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.43:8.3"
msgid "Dve paṭisambhidā dve vasā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.43:8.4"
msgid "duve niddasavatthunāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
